# hackocracy-terminals
Instructions To Run

1. Install Node version 8.3.0 on your system
2. Install mongodb version 3.4 or above on your system.
2. Download the folder/repo
3. Go to the directory (hackocracy-terminals) 
4. run this command to import the sites database to your system mongorestore -h localhost:27017 -d hackocracy abc/hackocracy/
5. run the command to start the app - "node app.js" (without quotes)
6. open browser and open site "localhost:3000"
7. Login to the site and post your queries see goverment posts -- have a say in the democracy of our country

